1
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:24,079
You wanna play music?!

2
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,640
You wanna play music?!

3
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:27,199
You wanna play music every day?!

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,399
Boss

5
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:45,920
We found Qibao

6
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:47,759
We found her

7
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:01,880
Qibao

8
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:02,759
Help me

9
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,359
What's wrong?

10
00:01:04,599 --> 00:01:05,200
Chen Hui

11
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,040
Who?

12
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:07,599
I'm so cold

13
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:08,400
Come here

14
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:09,680
I'm so cold

15
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,560
Qibao

16
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:13,719
You're finally awake

17
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,719
When you were kidnapped these past two days,

18
00:01:14,719 --> 00:01:16,239
Boss and I were scared to death

19
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:19,159
Kidnapped?

20
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,599
Yeah

21
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:23,959
After Guo Yi kidnapped you,

22
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:25,280
Boss got a call

23
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,920
demanding ten million in ransom

24
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:30,280
Chu Feng said it was two different groups

25
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,840
I don't really get it anyway

26
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:33,480
In short, all I can say is

27
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,439
you're safe now, and that's wonderful

28
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,680
I was really worried sick

29
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:37,959
Did my mom

30
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:39,879
pay the ransom to save me?

31
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,640
She insisted on delivering the money

32
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,959
I couldn't stop her

33
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,280
Two hundred thousand

34
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:47,519
just gone down the drain

35
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,519
Doctor

36
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,599
How's the patient Cao Li doing now?

37
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:58,640
His condition is fairly stable

38
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,719
He can be questioned now

39
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,120
Boss

40
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:13,360
Boss

41
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,120
Are you okay?

42
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:16,400
You

43
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:18,039
always making me worry

44
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:20,240
As if you actually cared about me

45
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:21,800
Qibao

46
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,000
Was it for the inheritance

47
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,080
that you faked all this to trick me?

48
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,120
Boss

49
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:27,360
Qibao just woke up, how can you...

50
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,159
That's right

51
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,080
I was just putting on an act

52
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,199
Locking myself in a freezer

53
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,039
and hitting myself

54
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:34,879
Don't believe me?

55
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:36,400
Go ask Guo Yi, who kidnapped me

56
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,960
He's my accomplice in this whole act

57
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,000
Is that really true?

58
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,039
How is that possible?

59
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,120
She's just saying that out of anger

60
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,560
That pervert Guo Yi,

61
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,120
was killed by someone

62
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,080
The police are investigating it right now

63
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:51,360
Cao Li

64
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,560
Cao Li

65
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:54,599
You're awake

66
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:56,719
Here

67
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,120
Take a look at this video

68
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,400
and see if you recognize anyone

69
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,719
Why is it him?

70
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,039
After killing someone,

71
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,599
he tried to kill me too.

72
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,319
Thankfully, you arrived

73
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:19,000
and scared him off.

74
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,000
Have you seen him before?

75
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,680
But he seemed to know Guo Yi.

76
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,319
He Siqi.

77
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,520
If you have something to say, say it properly.

78
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:35,280
You always lie. How can I trust you?

79
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,879
I think you've lost your mind.

80
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:38,759
Yes, I have lost my mind.

81
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,680
But it's you who drove me to it.

82
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:41,639
When I was little,

83
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:43,240
I didn't love dancing.

84
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,479
But to keep up appearances,

85
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,479
you forced me to learn.

86
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:47,439
But then,

87
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,879
I fell in love with dancing,

88
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,280
and with playing instruments.

89
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,240
Then you feared I wouldn't take over your business.

90
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,919
You'd rather destroy my dreams.

91
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,719
My life

92
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,240
was ruined by your own hands.

93
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,080
She destroyed everything I had,

94
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,879
and claimed it was for my own good.

95
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,319
That kind of "good,"

96
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,840
I'd rather do without.

97
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,400
To get back at me,

98
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,520
you broke into the safe,

99
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,120
stole the villa's property deed,

100
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,680
and demanded the inheritance.

101
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,319
You've put me through so much.

102
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,360
Haven't you let go of your anger yet?

103
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,639
Look at her.

104
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,040
She just refuses to admit she's wrong.

105
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,160
Fine, everything is my fault.

106
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,720
It's all on me.

107
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,439
I'm just an outsider.

108
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:30,360
I have no right to judge either of you.

109
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,079
Qibao,

110
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:33,120
Boss has admitted her fault and apologized.

111
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,040
Are you satisfied now?

112
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:34,720
Boss,

113
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,800
if Qibao obeys you,

114
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,879
will you finally be truly satisfied?

115
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:41,199
I couldn't care less about her apology.

116
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,399
See?

117
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:45,879
Nothing I do ever satisfies her.

118
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,639
You two really are mother and daughter.

119
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:50,439
Both of you are as stubborn as can be.

120
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,720
You don't understand anything.

121
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:53,680
I'd rather not have a mother like her.

122
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:56,480
You're right, I don't understand.

123
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,040
Because I lost my mom when I was seven.

124
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,120
In my whole life,

125
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,160
what I envied most

126
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,680
were kids who still had their moms.

127
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,720
You two are mother and daughter, after all.

128
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,439
If you don't cherish it now,

129
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,000
it'll be too late once she's gone.

130
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,959
I'm sorry.

131
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:18,360
I...

132
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,800
Was I too harsh just now?

133
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,279
Was I too hard on her?

134
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,000
Qibao, listen, Boss Bai...

135
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,040
deep down, she does care about you.

136
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,720
She just has a sharp tongue but a soft heart.

137
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,279
How about this?

138
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,279
You can lean on my shoulder.

139
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:38,879
Qibao,

140
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,560
but you have to promise me one thing.

141
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,560
From now on,

142
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,720
you can't hurt yourself like this anymore.

143
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,879
Hatred and revenge

144
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:46,560
won't solve anything.

145
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,959
You have to take care of yourself.

146
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,720
From now on,

147
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,279
let's look forward together.

148
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,600
This is the first time

149
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,279
I've ever seen you this serious.

150
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:02,560
Oh, right.

151
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,600
Just now,

152
00:06:04,439 --> 00:06:05,839
before you woke up,

153
00:06:05,959 --> 00:06:07,759
you kept calling out someone's name.

154
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:09,480
Chen Hui.

155
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:10,920
Who's that?

156
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,879
Well, just focus on recovering.

157
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:17,920
The doctor said

158
00:06:18,079 --> 00:06:19,720
your wife's recovery looks promising.

159
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:20,920
For her sake,

160
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,279
you have to pull yourself together.

161
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,079
I did wrong,

162
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:27,680
and I'll bear all legal responsibility.

163
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:29,360
From now on,

164
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,240
I'll take good care of Li Fang.

165
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,560
She will wake up. I'm sure of it.

166
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,639
Don't worry.

167
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,000
Just focus on getting better.

168
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,800
The blood analysis from Guo Yi's place is back.

169
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,639
There was more than one person at the scene.

170
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:55,480
So putting it all together, I deduce

171
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,439
Guo Yi illegally imprisoned He Siqi.

172
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,720
Then Ma Xiaojun

173
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,879
came to Guo Yi's house.

174
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,680
The two of them got into a fight.

175
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,120
Guo Yi subdued Ma Xiaojun

176
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,839
and took He Siqi to the cold storage.

177
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,639
Ma Xiaojun followed and killed Guo Yi.

178
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,720
But Guo Yi only had one phone,

179
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,879
and never made any ransom call

180
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:11,920
to Bai Ruifen.

181
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,480
As for Ma Xiaojun,

182
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,160
he's an online wanted fugitive.

183
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,920
He's been detained multiple times for fighting.

184
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,120
Later, while eating skewers,

185
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,000
he got into a fight with someone

186
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:20,079
and used an iron skewer

187
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,199
to seriously injure two people.

188
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,680
Ma Xiaojun fled right then.

189
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,399
Who would've thought

190
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,680
we'd run into him here.

191
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:25,720
Ma Xiaojun...

192
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,279
Why did he want to kill Guo Yi?

193
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,240
What's his connection with He Siqi?

194
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,759
Right now, only He Siqi knows the answer.

195
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:35,399
My dear lady,

196
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,879
I just asked you who Chen Hui is.

197
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,079
Fine, don't tell me then.

198
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:39,439
Why do you suddenly want to leave the hospital?

199
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,839
Is rambling and shouting names a crime?

200
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:43,600
I don't like being in the hospital.

201
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,720
I can't stay another day.

202
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,560
So where do you want to go?

203
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,439
I'll take you.

204
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:49,480
Can you stop following me?

205
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,519
You're stuck on me like glue.

206
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:51,959
You're injured right now,

207
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:53,680
so this glue's gotta stick to you.

208
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,560
Cling to you, stick to you.

209
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,319
Otherwise,

210
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,519
I'm afraid someone'll bully you.

211
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:57,199
I have to protect you.

212
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:57,680
Fine.

213
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,720
Then

214
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,199
I'll just treat you as my personal driver.

215
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:01,519
Let's set three ground rules.

216
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:02,399
First,

217
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,519
no asking where I'm going.

218
00:08:03,519 --> 00:08:04,360
No asking who I'm meeting.

219
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,079
Second,

220
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,279
no telling the police.

221
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,040
Third,

222
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,240
no snitching to my mom.

223
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:08,639
Deal.

224
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,560
So where are you going now?

225
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,120
Don't worry.

226
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,879
My lips are sealed.

227
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,120
I promise, no one can pry them open.

228
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:16,000
Okay, okay, okay.

229
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,480
Chen Hui.

230
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:27,360
Chen Dahui.

231
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,079
Who'd be dumb enough to be on the run for years

232
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,240
without even changing his last name?

233
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,440
Looks like this guy

234
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,559
is extremely confident.

235
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,480
He Siqi is trying to cover it up,

236
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,519
so there must be more to it.

237
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,799
Let's go ask her.

238
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,279
On the left.

239
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,600
Right here.

240
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,240
Here.

241
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:45,879
Yes.

242
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:48,679
Let's go.

243
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:54,879
Qibao.

244
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:02,159
Hey, where are you?

245
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:06,159
What?

246
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:08,080
Are you bringing people to arrest me?

247
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,799
Am I that kind of person?

248
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:11,080
I was afraid the police would track you down,

249
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,679
so I ran straight out of the hospital.

250
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:14,840
Do you know I almost got killed?

251
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,720
About what happened to you,

252
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,320
Xiaojun told me everything.

253
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,440
So...

254
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,080
you sent Ma Xiaojun to save me?

255
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:22,120
Then was he the one who killed Guo Yi?

256
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:22,919
Ma Xiaojun.

257
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:26,120
You're bringing a man with you now.

258
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,519
Are you afraid I'll kill you?

259
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,519
You don't trust me.

260
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,960
I've been protecting you in secret all along.

261
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:34,279
My mom had an inheritance.

262
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,720
Hardly anyone knew about it.

263
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:37,480
Guo Yi never mentioned it.

264
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:38,759
So...

265
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,240
he wasn't the one who kidnapped me.

266
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:42,919
So you really do suspect me.

267
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,720
Shouldn't I suspect you?

268
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,000
I didn't even know your name was Chen Dahui.

269
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,080
Where are you? Where the hell are you?

270
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,279
I need to talk to you face-to-face.

271
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:52,159
I want to clear this up in person.

272
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:52,919
Qibao.

273
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,080
Who are you looking for?

274
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,080
Who's Chen Dahui?

275
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,039
I know you're in there.

276
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,120
Get out here, now!

277
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,840
Come out!

278
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:02,679
I told you,

279
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:04,600
I'm the only one in the world who understands you,

280
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,759
who knows you and loves you.

281
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,279
I'm not stupid.

282
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,399
A loan shark like you is hardly innocent.

283
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:11,159
Tell me.

284
00:10:11,399 --> 00:10:12,559
Have you ever killed anyone or not?

285
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,559
That man you've got with you,

286
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,679
he's the Yu Tianfang you mentioned, right?

287
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:18,600
Why do you trust him to protect you,

288
